snippet.textDisplay:
Guys, you are not bound to listen this version of Rangabati folk songs. Watch/Listen something that you like. In fact you are free to do so. Someone is trying her best to represent out culture/songs on main stream. Its time to pull up your socks and appreciate for her effort so that many more such representation will be on your way and you will get the various tastes of music that can be refreshed you buds. At least do not blame for such attempts. There might be some corrections are required and the artists are ready to accept such corrections going forward. Please do not make it large and try to up your thumbs for it. 

Thanks,
An Odia being outside Odisha...
